<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<xliff xmlns="urn:oasis:names:tc:xliff:document:1.2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" version="1.2" xsi:schemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:xliff:document:1.2 xliff-core-1.2-transitional.xsd">
  <file datatype="xml" source-language="en" target-language="ko" original="../InitCommandStrings.resx">
    <body>
      <trans-unit id="AddingAppHostProjectToSolution">
        <source>Adding apphost project to solution...</source>
        <target state="translated">솔루션에 AppHost 프로젝트를 추가하는 중...</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="AddingProjectsToSolution">
        <source>Adding projects to solution...</source>
        <target state="translated">솔루션에 프로젝트를 추가하는 중...</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="AddingServiceDefaultsProjectToSolution">
        <source>Adding ServiceDefaults project to solution...</source>
        <target state="translated">솔루션에 ServiceDefaults 프로젝트를 추가하는 중...</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="AspireInitializationComplete">
        <source>Aspire initialization complete!</source>
        <target state="translated">Aspire 초기화 완료</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="CreatingAppHostProject">
        <source>Creating apphost project...</source>
        <target state="translated">AppHost 프로젝트를 만드는 중...</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="CreatingServiceDefaultsProject">
        <source>Creating ServiceDefaults project...</source>
        <target state="translated">ServiceDefaults 프로젝트를 만드는 중...</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="Description">
        <source>Initialize Aspire in an existing codebase</source>
        <target state="translated">기존 코드베이스에서 Aspire를 초기화합니다.</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="LanguageOptionDescription">
        <source>The programming language for the apphost (csharp, typescript)</source>
        <target state="translated">AppHost에 대한 프로그래밍 언어(csharp, typescript)</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="MultipleSolutionsFound">
        <source>Multiple solution files found. Please select which one to add the Aspire projects to:</source>
        <target state="translated">여러 솔루션 파일을 찾았습니다. Aspire 프로젝트를 추가할 항목을 선택하세요.</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="NoSolutionFoundCreatingSingleFileAppHost">
        <source>No solution file found. Creating single-file apphost...</source>
        <target state="translated">솔루션 파일을 찾을 수 없습니다. 단일 파일 AppHost를 만드는 중...</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="ResolvingTemplateVersion">
        <source>Resolving template version...</source>
        <target state="translated">템플릿 버전을 확인하는 중...</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="SolutionDetected">
        <source>Solution detected: {0}</source>
        <target state="translated">솔루션 검색됨: {0}</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="SolutionAlreadyInitialized">
        <source>Solution has already been initialized with Aspire.</source>
        <target state="translated">솔루션이 이미 Aspire로 초기화되었습니다.</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="SolutionAndProjectInSameDirectory">
        <source>The solution file '{0}' and project file '{1}' are in the same directory. The apphost and ServiceDefaults projects cannot be created inside an existing project directory. Move the solution file to a parent directory or the project file to a subdirectory.</source>
        <target state="translated">솔루션 파일 '{0}' 및 프로젝트 파일 '{1}'이(가) 동일한 디렉터리에 있습니다. AppHost 및 ServiceDefaults 프로젝트는 기존 프로젝트 디렉터리 내에 만들 수 없습니다. 솔루션 파일을 부모 디렉터리 또는 프로젝트 파일을 하위 디렉터리로 이동합니다.</target>
        <note />
      </trans-unit>
    </body>
  </file>
</xliff>